    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh i thought it was fine? a lot of health blogs say grapefruit juice is super good for you and helps with inflammation. i feel like it's just fruit so it's probably not going to do anything crazy to my meds. are you sure it's actually a big deal?",
